content: The Deathstinger Soak is one of the Rare Soaks for your Gourds in Black Myth: Wukong. The Soak's ability is punishing, actually dealing damage to yourself, making it not a useful option at all.

The content is as follows:
The Deathstinger Soak is one of the Rare Soaks for your Gourds in Black Myth: Wukong. The Soak's ability is punishing, actually dealing damage to yourself, making it not a useful option at all.
